# Test Implicit Context Passing Between Sessions
# This test verifies that sessions automatically see previous session outputs

# First session establishes some facts
session "I'm thinking of a number. It's 42. And my favorite color is blue. Remember these!"

# Second session should be able to reference the previous session without explicit context
session "What was the number and color I mentioned in my previous message? Answer briefly in format: 'Number: X, Color: Y'"

# Third session should see both previous sessions
session "How many messages have I sent so far? List the topics briefly."
